org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.adapter

Interface PersistentIndexFieldHandler<RowType,IndexFieldType extends CommonIndexValue,NativeFieldType>

  • Type Parameters:
    RowType -
    IndexFieldType -
    NativeFieldType -
    All Superinterfaces:
    IndexFieldHandler<RowType,IndexFieldType,NativeFieldType>, Persistable

    public interface PersistentIndexFieldHandler<RowType,IndexFieldType extends CommonIndexValue,NativeFieldType>
extends IndexFieldHandler<RowType,IndexFieldType,NativeFieldType>, Persistable
    This is a persistable version of the IndexFieldHandler so that customized field handlers can be automatically persisted with the data adapter. By default the field handlers assume that they can be recreated without custom serialization necessary but if it is necessary, the field handler should implement this interface.
